snippet: Vladimir Klitschko earned a unanimous points decision in a 12-round fight in Hamburg to retain his four title belts.
abstract: World heavyweight boxing champion Vladimir Klitschko defeats Mariusz Wach in 12 rounds by unanimous decision to retain his four title belts.
lead_paragraph: Vladimir Klitschko earned a unanimous points decision in a 12-round fight in Hamburg to retain his four title belts.

headline.seo: Vladimir Klitschko Earns Unanimous Decision to Retain Belts
